OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fwith late sunny spells but soon
OL,7,Fturning cloudy with rain pushing into
OL,8,Fthe north of Aberdeenshire. Mostly
OL,9,Fcloudy and dry overnight with rain
OL,10,Faround northern coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy but mostly
OL,13,Fdry day, with occasional bright or
OL,14,Fsunny intervals. Thicker cloud in the
OL,15,Fnorth with some light rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
