OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly dry on Thursday with variable
OL,7,Fcloud and sunny spells. Then becoming
OL,8,Fmostly cloudy on Friday and Saturday
OL,9,Fwith some outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,10,Feastwards.
